# Track-Futura Project Overview

## What is Track-Futura?
Track-Futura is a comprehensive social media analytics and data collection platform that enables users to scrape, analyze, and generate reports from multiple social media platforms including Facebook, Instagram, LinkedIn, and TikTok.

## Core Functionality
- **Data Collection**: Automated scraping of social media content using BrightData API
- **Multi-Platform Analytics**: Support for Facebook, Instagram, LinkedIn, TikTok
- **Report Generation**: Customizable reports with data visualization
- **Real-time Monitoring**: Live data collection and webhook processing
- **User Management**: Multi-tenant system with user authentication
- **Data Export**: CSV export capabilities for all collected data

## Technology Stack
- **Backend**: Django REST Framework, Python, SQLite
- **Frontend**: React 18, TypeScript, Material-UI, Tailwind CSS
- **Data Processing**: Pandas, NumPy
- **Visualization**: Chart.js, Recharts
- **External APIs**: BrightData for web scraping

## Key Business Logic
- Users can create projects to organize their data collection efforts
- Each social media platform has dedicated data models and scraping workflows
- Scraping jobs are managed asynchronously with webhook callbacks
- Reports can be generated from collected data with various filtering options
- Real-time chat functionality for collaboration

## Database Structure
- User and authentication models
- Platform-specific data models (FacebookPost, InstagramPost, etc.)
- Project and folder organization models
- Scraping job tracking models
- Report and analytics models

## External Integrations
- **BrightData API**: Primary scraping service
- **Webhook Processing**: Real-time job status updates
- **File Handling**: CSV imports/exports, file uploads
